---
---

<section id="sobre-nosotros" class="relative py-24 md:py-32 bg-brand-bg overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Subtle organic background shapes -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-20">
    <div class="absolute top-[20%] -right-[15%] w-[45%] h-[55%] bg-brand-champagne-light clip-leaf-right blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-[10%] left-[5%] w-[40%] h-[50%] bg-brand-sage-light clip-leaf-left blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 lg:gap-12 items-center">
      
      <!-- Collage Visual (Left Column) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-6 order-last lg:order-first relative flex items-center justify-center min-h-[450px] md:min-h-[500px]">
        <!-- Abstract shape decoration -->
        <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-72 h-72 bg-brand-sage-light/50 clip-leaf-left -z-10 animate-pulse-soft"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-8 right-8 w-64 h-64 bg-brand-champagne-light/60 clip-leaf-right -z-10"></div>

        <!-- Background Offset Card (Champagne Tone) -->
        <div class="absolute left-4 top-12 w-[70%] aspect-square bg-brand-champagne/10 rounded-3xl border border-brand-champagne/20 shadow-sm -rotate-3 z-0"></div>

        <!-- Main Product/Botany Image Frame -->
        <div class="relative w-[75%] aspect-square rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden shadow-xl border-4 border-white/80 z-10 transform hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-500 clip-leaf-left">
          <img 
            src="/images/about_skincare.png" 
            alt="Ingredientes de cosmética orgánica Aura" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>

        <!-- Floating Glassmorphic Infocard -->
        <div class="absolute bottom-6 right-0 md:right-4 max-w-[240px] p-5 glass-luxe-light rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-white/40 z-20 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
          <span class="block font-display text-2xl font-light text-brand-sage-dark mb-1">100%</span>
          <span class="block font-sans text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-dark mb-1">Médicos Certificados</span>
          <span class="block font-sans text-[11px] text-brand-dark-soft leading-relaxed">Nuestros tratamientos son aplicados exclusivamente por profesionales médicos diplomados.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Copy Content Area (Right Column) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-6 flex flex-col space-y-8">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <!-- Muted Label -->
          <span class="font-sans text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-semibold text-brand-sage-dark">Nuestra Filosofía</span>
          
          <!-- Heading -->
          <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light tracking-tight leading-[1.15] text-brand-dark">
            La medicina estética como una expresión de <span class="font-medium italic text-brand-sage-dark">armonía y respeto</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6 font-sans text-brand-dark-soft font-light leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Creemos firmemente que la mejor medicina estética es aquella que <strong class="font-medium text-brand-dark">no se nota</strong>. No buscamos transformar tu rostro, sino restaurar los volúmenes, suavizar las líneas de cansancio y reavivar la luminosidad natural que el tiempo atenúa.
          </p>
          <p>
            En Aura, cada protocolo es diseñado a medida después de una rigurosa consulta de diagnóstico. Nos basamos en la anatomía individual para aplicar dosis precisas y técnicas de vanguardia que garantizan la máxima seguridad y resultados elegantes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Strategic Bullet Pillars -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 pt-6 border-t border-brand-sage/15">
          <!-- Pillar 1 -->
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-none w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-sage/10 border border-brand-sage/20 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-sage-dark">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 01-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0112 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 01-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 013 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 011.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 013.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0112 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 013.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 011.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0121 12z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-1">
              <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-brand-dark">Naturalidad Primero</h3>
              <p class="font-sans text-xs text-brand-dark-soft/90">Tratamientos sutiles diseñados para realzar, nunca para distorsionar.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Pillar 2 -->
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-none w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-sage/10 border border-brand-sage/20 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-sage-dark">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.42 15.17L17.25 21A1.79 1.79 0 0021 19.75V11.42L15.17 17.25M3 11.42V19.75A1.79 1.79 0 006.75 21L12.58 15.17L6.75 9.33" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-1">
              <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-brand-dark">Ciencia Médica</h3>
              <p class="font-sans text-xs text-brand-dark-soft/90">Equipamiento aprobado por ANMAT y productos de laboratorios internacionales.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
